          "text": "Discussion",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This command sets, or clears, a password on booting to recoveryOS. When the device unenrolls MDM the system removes the recovery password.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This command is only available with Apple silicon.",
              "type": "text"
            }
